ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nE-MAIL又大条道理唔覆客。<br />\n結果做能到我仆街<br />\n部長巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實而家日本人係咪冇以前咁盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係！年軽世代無責任。<br />\n50才以上好好多、交報告内容詳細、有方向去推進一件事。<br />\n年軽一班報告得三、四行字、完全等指示叫一様野做一様野。"},{"pid":"eb52f34f4afb9cafd6802e1d1f577bd790402152","tid":2500143,"uid":111977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818c7751ef0fa5ff37aab5604eab6969c75b3498","tid":2500143,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"089ed0e15b3ce0b1dc4dd57c9b367f100028feab","tid":2500143,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"151e5a02f42a7b640447d67a64cd7254e2d2d990","tid":2500143,"uid":111977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:23:55.000Z","msg":"日本真係玩就ok<br />\n住就pk <br />\n啲鄰里關係煩到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"日本韓國都係for fun一流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"剩係睇武肺處理手法都死啦"},{"pid":"468439fac3cf2ae73a6e622bd42b402319a47bba","tid":2500143,"uid":39303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"2330今日咁撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75416b42fd06168f4938e3fbceffa8086ee9a6c","tid":2500143,"uid":239825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07acccd3e24805b5725dceeaf72e2bf1342ef718","tid":2500143,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb52f34f4afb9cafd6802e1d1f577bd790402152","tid":2500143,"uid":111977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818c7751ef0fa5ff37aab5604eab6969c75b3498","tid":2500143,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":